{"tid":1290311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普擬行政命令降美國藥價　與世界最低水平看齊","createTime":"2019-07-06T12:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:19:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"06f05ee4f79dc574ed07fd7f7006cf31f41ea5e3","tid":1290311,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"特朗普擬行政命令降美國藥價　與世界最低水平看齊 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190706/s00005/1562384755973/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e6%93%ac%e8%a1%8c%e6%94%bf%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4%e9%99%8d%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%97%a5%e5%83%b9-%e8%88%87%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e5%b9%b3%e7%9c%8b%e9%bd%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190706%2Fs00005%2F1562384755973%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e6%2593%25ac%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%2591%25bd%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e9%2599%258d%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%2597%25a5%25e5%2583%25b9-%25e8%2588%2587%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e6%259c%2580%25e4%25bd%258e%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%25b9%25b3%25e7%259c%258b%25e9%25bd%258a&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=8cee0e5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190706%2Fs00005%2F1562384755973%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e6%2593%25ac%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%2591%25bd%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e9%2599%258d%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%2597%25a5%25e5%2583%25b9-%25e8%2588%2587%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e6%259c%2580%25e4%25bd%258e%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%25b9%25b3%25e7%259c%258b%25e9%25bd%258a&h=7f3ec813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190706/s00005/1562384755973/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e6%93%ac%e8%a1%8c%e6%94%bf%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4%e9%99%8d%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%97%a5%e5%83%b9-%e8%88%87%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e5%b9%b3%e7%9c%8b%e9%bd%8a</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周五（5日）表示，政府正擬定一道行政命令，降低美國藥價，與世界最低藥價看齊。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，多年來其他國家的藥價都比美國低，有時低上60%、70%。他批評，製藥公司「長久以來佔了這個體系的便宜」，讓美國藥價經常高於鄰近的加拿大、墨西哥和歐洲，質疑爲何其他國家可以比美國付少些錢。他表示，將以行政命令的方式來處理這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，由本月開始，美國政府將要求製藥公司在電視廣告中披露藥價。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）"},{"pid":"bb7e29f57561209c729bed45a16a0ea089e62daa","tid":1290311,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":41,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實，關我撚事"},{"pid":"e5a0b903ab66c1aa0c1bcf6507b7a188812eafc4","tid":1290311,"uid":51724,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"其實只要全世界都賣到美國一樣貴，咁就公平勒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5840cdfb5a6305bc466caf7c4682a8bbb1313e","tid":1290311,"uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bb7e29f57561209c729bed45a16a0ea089e62daa","tid":1290311,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":41,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實，關我撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"Ching成世唔駛食藥？"},{"pid":"47778e53e3b6372e3142d58b2efb07bb756dd631","tid":1290311,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"民主黨唔使派人選了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b30dfcced8e086e0fdcdca91e95a67378842450","tid":1290311,"uid":22736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bb7e29f57561209c729bed45a16a0ea089e62daa","tid":1290311,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":41,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實，關我撚事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"你條撚遲早要食偉哥咁關唔關你事"},{"pid":"02100d9b0494da1e6961bc83daf11ddfbd902b7d","tid":1290311,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl